[% major_ver = "1.15.8"; version = major_ver _ ".4" %]
OpenResty [% version %] is a patch release addressing a recent security
vulnerability the ngx_http_lua module.

The (portable) source code distribution, the Win32/Win64 binary
distributions, and the pre-built binary Linux packages for Ubuntu,
Debian, Fedora, CentOS, RHEL, OpenSUSE, Amazon Linux are provided on this
page:

https://openresty.org/en/download.html

This is the fourth OpenResty release based on the nginx [% major_ver %] core.

# Acknowledgments

Thanks Thibault Charbonnier and Dejiang Zhu for helping this release.

# Full Changelog

Complete change logs since the last (formal) release, 1.15.8.3, can be browsed
