# Feedback

Feedback on this release is more than welcome. Feel free to create new [GitHub
issues](https://github.com/openresty/openresty/issues) or send emails to one of
our [mailing lists](community.html).

# The Next Release

The next release will be OpenResty 1.17.8.1 based on the recent nginx 1.17.8
core and its RC1 version is already out for community testing. See

https://openresty.org/en/ann-1017008001rc1.html
